This package is still under development. If you find a bug (especially under Windows), or if you have any criticisms/questions about this package, then please feel free to email the package developer.  I am grateful to  Prof Brian Ripley and Sergey Fedorov for reporting bugs and making suggestions that  I have been developing neojags.  Thanks also to Martyn Plummer for developing JAGS, Matthew Denwood for developing runjags, Mikis Stasinopoulos et.al. for developing gamlss.dist


